## Dynamic Blocks

### Basic Usage

```hcl
resource "oci_core_security_list" "web" {
  compartment_id = var.compartment_id
  vcn_id         = oci_core_vcn.vcn.id
  display_name   = "web-security-list"

  dynamic "egress_security_rule" {
    for_each = var.allowed_cidrs
    content {
      destination = egress_security_rule.value
      protocol    = "6"
    }
  }
}
```

### Nested Dynamic

```hcl
dynamic "ingress_security_rule" {
  for_each = var.ingress_rules
  content {
    protocol = ingress_security_rule.value.protocol

    dynamic "tcp_options" {
      for_each = ingress_security_rule.value.ports
      content {
        min = tcp_options.value.min
        max = tcp_options.value.max
      }
    }
  }
}
```

### Use Cases

- Security rules
- Multiple blocks
- Repetitive config
